# Manim Project Conventions

- Default preview: `manim render -pql <file> <SceneName>`
- Final render: `manim render -pqh <file> <SceneName>`
- Never commit `media/` or generated partial movie files
- Use Pango text for labels/titles; LaTeX (MathTex) for mathematical notation
- Scene classes must be self-contained and importable
- Keep reusable mobject helpers in `lib/`
- Use only installed font family names (no relative font paths)
- Do not introduce absolute paths in scene code
- Lint with ruff, not flake8 or pylint
- Format with ruff, not black or prettier
- Type hints required for all helper functions
